{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8f6b4bc3d2","title":"国务院关于淮南问题的通知","origin":"原载北京化工学院毛泽东思想宣传员 《无产阶级文化大革命文件汇编 [第二集]》，北京：1967年9月","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"318c4aa9f3","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":18,"articleId":"8f6b4bc3d2"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"30d36ead2a","type":"title","text":"国务院关于淮南问题的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8f6b4bc3d2"},{"id":"44bf037d19","type":"appellation","text":"省军管会、市军管会、方仲林同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8f6b4bc3d2"},{"id":"47bb32109a","type":"paragraph","text":"1.目前6375部队决不能参加武斗。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8f6b4bc3d2"},{"id":"efae0025ff","type":"paragraph","text":"2.昨日高鹏带支临派回淮南，到达时要说服他们支临派立即停止武斗，双方要严格执行六项协议。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8f6b4bc3d2"},{"id":"a4a1d520a9","type":"paragraph","text":"3.炮轰派不是牛鬼蛇神，不是反革命，而是革命群众组织，不能对他们采取镇压手段。此事要向群众宣布。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8f6b4bc3d2"},{"id":"30b7e00e5d","type":"paragraph","text":"4.两名记者如有困难，望同杜重山一道回北京。明天中午中央派直升飞机到淮南散发六项协议和通知。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8f6b4bc3d2"},{"id":"a427b8f727","type":"paragraph","text":" 国务院一九六七年七月十八日","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8f6b4bc3d2"}],"page":{"id":"bbab7bfb64","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8f6b4bc3d2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}